\v 1 \w TO|strong="H5921"\w* \w THE|strong="H5921"\w* OVERSEER. [SET] \w ON|strong="H5921"\w* “DOE \w OF|strong="H4210"\w* \w THE|strong="H5921"\w* \w MORNING|strong="H7837"\w*.” \w A|strong="H3068"\w* \w PSALM|strong="H4210"\w* \w OF|strong="H4210"\w* \w DAVID|strong="H1732"\w*. \w My|strong="H1732"\w* God, \w My|strong="H1732"\w* God, \w why|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H5921"\w* \w You|strong="H5921"\w* forsaken \w Me|strong="H5921"\w*? \w Far|strong="H5921"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w My|strong="H1732"\w* salvation, || \w The|strong="H5921"\w* words \w of|strong="H4210"\w* \w My|strong="H1732"\w* roaring?
