\v 5 Behold, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3045"\w* been brought \w forth|strong="H3045"\w* \w in|strong="H3045"\w* iniquity, || \w And|strong="H3045"\w* \w my|strong="H3045"\w* mother conceives \w me|strong="H5048"\w* \w in|strong="H3045"\w* \w sin|strong="H2403"\w*.
