\v 1 \w TO|strong="H5921"\w* \w THE|strong="H5921"\w* OVERSEER. “\w ON|strong="H5921"\w* \w A|strong="H3068"\w* DISEASE.” \w AN|strong="H5921"\w* INSTRUCTION \w OF|strong="H5921"\w* \w DAVID|strong="H1732"\w*. \w A|strong="H3068"\w* fool said \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* heart, “There \w is|strong="H1732"\w* no God.” \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H5921"\w* done corruptly, || Indeed, \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H5921"\w* done abominable iniquity, || There \w is|strong="H1732"\w* none doing good.
