\v 1 \w TO|strong="H1732"\w* \w THE|strong="H1732"\w* OVERSEER. \w WITH|strong="H1732"\w* \w STRINGED|strong="H5058"\w* \w INSTRUMENTS|strong="H5058"\w*. \w AN|strong="H1732"\w* INSTRUCTION \w OF|strong="H4905"\w* \w DAVID|strong="H1732"\w*. Give ear, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* God, [\w to|strong="H1732"\w*] \w my|strong="H1732"\w* prayer, || \w And|strong="H1732"\w* do \w not|strong="H1732"\w* hide from \w my|strong="H1732"\w* supplication.
