\v 1 \w TO|strong="H1732"\w* \w THE|strong="H1732"\w* OVERSEER. “DO \w NOT|strong="H1732"\w* DESTROY.” \w A|strong="H3068"\w* MIKTAM \w OF|strong="H4387"\w* \w DAVID|strong="H1732"\w*. \w Is|strong="H1732"\w* it true, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* silent one, \w that|strong="H1732"\w* you speak righteously? Do you judge uprightly, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* sons \w of|strong="H4387"\w* men?
